:"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32714,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/07\/cures-physical-mental-spiritual\/","url_meta":{"origin":32706,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Healing: Cures for every physical, mental, spiritual disease","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah did not send down any disease but that he also sent down the cure.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5354 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Bukhari Ibn al-Qayyim said, \u201cThis is generally true for diseases of the heart, the spirit, the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17563,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/11\/best-thing-khuluq-hasan-adab\/","url_meta":{"origin":32706,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: Good character best thing given by Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 11, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Usamah ibn Sharik reported: I witnessed bedouins ask the Prophet, saying, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is the best thing a servant may be given?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGood character.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3436 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e